OL,6,F"We haven't got guarantees or
OL,7,Fpromises. It's been really difficult.
OL,8,FWe're living in a room and at the
OL,9,Fhote, we've got no fridge, we've got
OL,10,Fno cooking facilities, nothing.J"So
OL,11,Fit's been really difficult. We're
OL,12,Fthere with my daughter who's a nurse
OL,13,Fwho's been working long shifts."
