OL,6,FShe says these drains and ditches pose
OL,7,Fa flooding risk across Wales if they
OL,8,Fare neglected, forgotten or
OL,9,Fresponsibility is unclear.
OL,11,FShe said: "Flooding is a big issue. I
OL,12,Fwant to make homeowners more resilient
OL,13,Fagainst flooding. It can happen really
OL,14,Fsuddenly overnight.
OL,16,F"When it happens, it's devastating.
OL,17,FPeople very often phone the council up
OL,18,Finstead of the fire service because
OL,19,Fthey just don't know what to do to get
OL,20,Fhelp.
