OL,3,CThe woman living in a hotel for 17
OL,4,Cweeks after her home was flooded
OL,6,F"They are asking for sandbags. But
OL,7,Fcouncils nowadays won't provide
OL,8,Fsandbags.J"They haven't got the
OL,9,Ffunding to do so. So homeowners need
OL,10,Fto do things themselves to be more
OL,11,Fresilient and to be prepared.
OL,13,F"But I'm also asking that landowners
OL,14,Fwho have got ditches and culverts will
OL,15,Fbe responsible for them, not the
OL,16,Fcouncil, that they will maintain them
OL,17,Fproperly."
